  <zone type="main">
    <line>Chap. 11</line>
    <milestone unit="tei:p"/>
    <line>We were soon joined <mod type="subst"><del rend="cross-hatch">B</del><del
          rend="triple-strike">y</del><add place="sublinear">&#x2038;</add><add place="superlinear"
          >by</add></mod> Elizabeth. Time</line>
    <line>had made great alterations in her form since</line>
    <line>I had last beheld her. Five years <del rend="strikethrough">ago</del> before</line>
    <line>she was a pretty, good humoured girl <delSpan spanTo="#c56-0090.01"/>with an</line>
    <line>understanding above her years<anchor xml:id="c56-0090.01"/> Whom every</line>
    <line>one loved, and <mod type="subst"><del rend="strikethrough">humoured</del><add
          place="superlinear">caressed</add></mod>. She was now a woman</line>
    <line>in stature and expression of countenance</line>
    <line>which was uncommonly lovely – An open &amp;</line>
    <line>capacious for<mod type="additions"><add place="sublinear">&#x2038;</add><add
          place="superlinear">e</add></mod>head gave indications of a good</line>
    <line>understanding joined to great frankness. Her</line>
    <line>eyes were hazel and <delSpan spanTo="#c56-0090.02"/>very soft now through</line>
    <line>recent affliction they expressed sorrow. Her</line>
    <line>smile had som<anchor xml:id="c56-0090.02"/> expressive <mod type="subst"><del
          rend="strikethrough">great</del><add place="sublinear">&#x2038;</add><add
          place="superlinear">of uncommon</add></mod> mildness now</line>
    <line>through recent affliction allied to sadness–</line>
    <line>Her hair was of a rich <mod type="subst"><add place="sublinear">&#x2038;</add><add
          place="superlinear">dark</add> auburn and <add place="sublinear">&#x2038;</add><add
          place="superlinear">her complexion fair</add></mod> her</line>
    <line>figure sli<add place="intralinear" resp="#pbs">ght</add> and graceful. She <mod
        type="deletions" xml:id="c56-0090.03" next="#c56-0090.04"><del rend="strikethrough"
          >embraced</del></mod></line>
    <line><mod type="deletions" prev="#c56-0090.03" xml:id="c56-0090.04"><del rend="cross-hatch"
          >w</del>
        <del rend="strikethrough">me with</del></mod> welcomed me with the greatest</line>
    <line>affection <milestone unit="tei:q" spanTo="#c56-0090.05"/><metamark>"</metamark>Your
      arrival, my <mod type="subst"><del rend="strikethrough">best</del><add place="superlinear"
          >dearest</add></mod> cousin,<metamark>"</metamark><anchor xml:id="c56-0090.05"/></line>
    <line>said she, give <milestone unit="tei:q" spanTo="#c56-0090.06"/><metamark>"</metamark>fills
      me with hope. You</line>
    <line>perhaps will find out some means to</line>
    <line>justify my poor <mod type="subst"><del rend="strikethrough">innocent</del><add
          place="sublinear">&#x2038;</add><add place="superlinear">guiltless</add></mod> Justine.
      Alas</line>
    <line>Who is safe is she were convicted <mod type="subst"><add place="sublinear"
          >&#x2038;</add><add place="superlinear" resp="#pbs">of crime?</add><del
          rend="strikethrough">for</del></mod></line>
    <line>I <del rend="strikethrough">belie</del> rely on <del rend="strikethrough">her</del> her
      innocence as cer</line> Our <line>tainly as I do <add place="intralinear" resp="#pbs"
        >upon</add> my own. <add place="superlinear">Our</add> Misfortune is</line>
    <line>doubly hard to us. <mod type="subst"><add place="superlinear">We</add><del
          rend="cross-hatch">I</del></mod> have not only lost</line>
    <line>that lovely darling boy but this poor girl</line>
    <line>whom I sincerely love, is to be torn</line>
